rce/French_language\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"complete weirdos\", \"from\": 1469, \"to\": 1485}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We all know that,\\\" Stefanovic said.\", \"from\": 1487, \"to\": 1522, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Stefanovic\", \"from\": 1506, \"to\": 1516}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"They are kind of a weird nation, sexually.\\\"\", \"from\": 1524, \"to\": 1568, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"kind of a weird nation\", \"from\": 1534, \"to\": 1556}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Stefanovic said he had \\\"stopped trying\\\" to learn French and came clean that he did not really \\\"like them that much\\\".\", \"from\": 1570, \"to\": 1686, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1619, \"end\": 1625, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9956386326287546, \"rank\": 0.0029579605722813524, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Stefanovic\", \"from\": 1570, \"to\": 1580}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"They are so rude.\", \"from\": 1688, \"to\": 1706, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Oh, they are really up themselves... they are pompous.\", \"from\": 1707, \"to\": 1761, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"They do a good burger though.\", \"from\": 1762, \"to\": 1791, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a good burger\", \"from\": 1770, \"to\": 1783}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I do like the burgers and stuff over here,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 1792, \"to\": 1844, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the burgers\", \"from\": 1802, \"to\": 1813}, {\"ngram\": \"stuff\", \"from\": 1818, \"to\": 1823}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, McGuire said the rule-dominated city of Melbourne needed an overhaul, and to take a leaf from the French with their 'no rules apply' attitude.\", \"from\": 1846, \"to